{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Remediated plan-review run 1 (BLOCK: 9 blocking / 20 advisory) + folded in the b744 code-review worktree ground-truth. Design edits: (1) concrete .rebar/criteria_routing.json overlay schema — gate-keyed, project.<name> namespace, load-time collision/rebind rejection, explicit 'activate' list (E2/G6/T8); (2) open the closed vocabularies CANONICAL_LLM + OVERLAY_IDS via effective_criteria(repo_root) — the true precondition (G6); (3) cache isolation (packaged cached, overlay uncached/mtime-keyed) + RED cross-repo-leak test (G6); (4) Attestation section — registry_version(repo_root) hashes the overlay, disable-in-coverage, expand-contract back-compat, cross-gate AC8 (G6/COH/E1); (5) DET scan scoping + LLM-block fail-open, reconciled with no-baseline (COH); (6) risk-ordered MVP build order (G5); (7) migration/compat — preserve review_code/shim.py review_result shape. Ground-truth resizes: story 3 mostly built (code_review/detectors.py via shared engine_b.scan+load_registry; generalize the hardcoded security prefix); per-criterion blocking DONE (threshold_for + kernel Pass-3); story 5 = attestation port only; review_kernel already shared by both gates. Re-running review-plan."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782868372807897001,"uuid":"b60fabf8-776b-4896-b04f-19f290861031"}